<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Name - Resume</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css">
    <style>
        /* Base styles */
body {
  font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  background-color: #f8f9fa;
  color: #333;
}

.container {
  max-width: 850px;
  margin: 40px auto;
  background-color: #fff;
  padding: 50px;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  border-radius: 8px;
}

/* Typography */
h1, h2, h3 {
  font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  margin-top: 0;
}

h1 {
  color: #2c3e50;
  font-size: 2.5em;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}

h2 {
  color: #3498db;
  font-size: 1.8em;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
  padding-bottom: 10px;
  margin-top: 40px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

h3 {
  color: #34495e;
  font-size: 1.3em;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}

/* Header */
header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  padding-bottom: 20px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
}

.contact-info {
  color: #7f8c8d;
  font-size: 0.95em;
  margin-top: 15px;
}

/* Sections */
.section {
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

/* Lists */
ul {
  padding-left: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

li {
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

/* Job Experience */
.job {
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.job-title {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #2c3e50;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.job-date {
  font-style: italic;
  color: #7f8c8d;
  font-size: 0.9em;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

/* Education */
.education-item {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

/* Skills */
.skills-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
  list-style-type: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.skills-list li {
  background-color: #3498db;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 8px 15px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-size: 0.9em;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.skills-list li:hover {
  background-color: #2980b9;
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .container {
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 20px;
  }

  h1 {
      font-size: 2em;
  }

  h2 {
      font-size: 1.5em;
  }
}

/* Print styles */
@media print {
  body {
      background-color: #fff;
  }

  .container {
      box-shadow: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
  }

  .skills-list li {
      border: 1px solid #3498db;
      color: #3498db;
      background-color: transparent;
  }
}

/* Additional enhancements */
.section p {
  text-align: justify;
}

.highlight {
  background-color: #f1c40f;
  padding: 2px 5px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.subtitle {
  color: #7f8c8d;
  font-size: 1.1em;
  margin-top: -5px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.icon {
  margin-right: 8px;
  color: #3498db;
}

.button {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background-color: #3498db;
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.button:hover {
  background-color: #2980b9;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1><%= name %></h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Professional Title</p>
            <p class="contact-info">
                <span class="icon">üìß</span>  <%= email %>
                <span class="icon">üì±</span> <%= phone %>
                <span class="icon">üìç</span> <%= address %>
            </p>
        </header>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Summary</h2>
            <p>A brief, compelling summary of your professional background and career objectives. Highlight your <span class="highlight">key strengths</span> and what makes you unique in your field.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Experience</h2>
            <div class="job">
                <h3 class="job-title">Senior Position, Company Name</h3>
                <p class="job-date">January 2020 - Present</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Key responsibility or notable achievement with quantifiable results</li>
                    <li>Another significant contribution to the company or team</li>
                    <li>Implemented new process that improved efficiency by <span class="highlight">25%</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="job">
                <h3 class="job-title">Previous Role, Previous Company Name</h3>
                <p class="job-date">June 2015 - December 2019</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Major accomplishment that added value to the company</li>
                    <li>Led a team project that resulted in significant improvements</li>
                    <li>Received recognition for outstanding performance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Education</h2>
            <div class="education-item">
                <h3>Master of Science in Relevant Field</h3>
                <p>University Name, Graduation Year</p>
            </div>
            <div class="education-item">
                <h3>Bachelor of Arts in Another Relevant Field</h3>
                <p>University Name, Graduation Year</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Skills</h2>
            <ul class="skills-list">
                <li>Skill 1</li>
                <li>Skill 2</li>
                <li>Skill 3</li>
                <li>Skill 4</li>
                <li>Skill 5</li>
                <li>Skill 6</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Awards & Certifications</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Relevant Industry Award, Year</li>
                <li>Professional Certification, Issuing Organization, Year</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <div class="section">
            <a href="#" class="button">Download Full Resume</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>